high_descs: Go to the right and stand in front of the computer.
Shut the computer and pick it up from the table.
Go to the left and then left again to face the blue chair.
Put the computer on the blue chair.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the laptop on the shelves near the wall.
Pick up the laptop from the top shelf.
Turn around and walk to the blue armchair in the corner of the room.
Put the laptop on the seat of the armchair.
anns.task_desc: Move a laptop from a shelf to an armchair.
